        "faq_item_aWG7qk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Information on products and prices",
            "faq_answer": "<p>The prices provided by ZIPPY include the tax applicable by law (VAT). Any changes to the said tax will reflect immediately on the prices practiced by the brand. Nevertheless, ZIPPY reserves the right to change its prices at any given time, and items may be available for limited periods of time established by the brand.<br/> <br/>The user is responsible for any shipping costs, unless otherwise established by the brand.<br/> <br/>Considering that ZIPPY is responsible for a wide range of articles, keep in mind that labelling is not error-free. In cases where errors are detected during the order treatment process, the buyer is free to reconfirm his order at the correct price or cancel such order.</p>",
            "list_1": "",
